{"note_id": "note_tc_001", "type": "normal", "title": "ins风防水桌布推荐｜奶油色系太绝了", "desc": "这款奶油风桌布真的太好看了！防水防油免洗，拍照超出片。PVC材质好打理，尺寸可以定制，圆桌方桌都适配。价格也很平价，性价比很高，买了不会踩坑。家里茶几餐桌都换上了，氛围感拉满。推荐给想改造桌面的姐妹们！", "video_url": "", "time": 1743580800, "last_update_time": 0, "user_id": "u001", "nickname": "家居博主小A", "avatar": "https://example.com/avatar1.jpg", "liked_count": "328", "collected_count": "156", "comment_count": "42", "share_count": "18", "ip_location": "广东", "image_list": "https://example.com/img1.jpg,https://example.com/img2.jpg", "tag_list": "桌布,ins风,家居好物,防水桌布", "last_modify_ts": 1743580900000, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/note_tc_001", "source_keyword": "桌布", "xsec_token": "token001"}
{"note_id": "note_tc_002", "type": "normal", "title": "北欧棉麻桌布测评｜质感真的很高级", "desc": "入了三款北欧风棉麻桌布做对比测评。这款棉麻材质手感很好，颜色也很正。缺点是不防水，容易脏需要经常洗。适合拍照出片但不太实用。如果家里有小孩建议选防水款。尺寸方面长桌款偏大，需要注意量好尺寸再买。价格中等偏贵，但质感值这个价。", "video_url": "", "time": 1743494400, "last_update_time": 0, "user_id": "u002", "nickname": "生活家小B", "avatar": "https://example.com/avatar2.jpg", "liked_count": "512", "collected_count": "234", "comment_count": "67", "share_count": "31", "ip_location": "上海", "image_list": "https://example.com/img3.jpg,https://example.com/img4.jpg,https://example.com/img5.jpg", "tag_list": "桌布,北欧风,棉麻,测评", "last_modify_ts": 1743494500000, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/note_tc_002", "source_keyword": "餐桌布", "xsec_token": "token002"}
{"note_id": "note_tc_003", "type": "normal", "title": "桌垫选购攻略｜防水防油真的太重要了", "desc": "用了好几款桌垫总结的选购经验。防水防油是第一要素，免洗好打理才是王道。PVC和硅胶材质都不错，棉麻好看但真的不实用。推荐这款防水桌垫，便宜又好用，性价比绝了。茶几桌布也可以用同款，尺寸很全。唯一的坑是色差，实物比图片偏暗。", "video_url": "", "time": 1743408000, "last_update_time": 0, "user_id": "u003", "nickname": "收纳达人C", "avatar": "https://example.com/avatar3.jpg", "liked_count": "891", "collected_count": "445", "comment_count": "103", "share_count": "56", "ip_location": "北京", "image_list": "https://example.com/img6.jpg", "tag_list": "桌垫,防水,家居", "last_modify_ts": 1743408100000, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/note_tc_003", "source_keyword": "桌垫", "xsec_token": "token003"}
{"note_id": "note_tc_004", "type": "video", "title": "餐桌改造vlog｜换了桌布整个餐厅都不一样了", "desc": "花30块改造餐桌！换了一张奶油风防水桌布，整个餐厅氛围感直接拉满。拍照上镜效果超好，法式复古风格太绝了。之前的桌面又旧又丑，现在朋友来都夸好看。桌布尺寸刚好，方桌圆桌都有卖。真的是小成本大改造的典范！", "video_url": "https://example.com/video1.mp4", "time": 1743321600, "last_update_time": 0, "user_id": "u004", "nickname": "改造狂人D", "avatar": "https://example.com/avatar4.jpg", "liked_count": "1523", "collected_count": "678", "comment_count": "189", "share_count": "92", "ip_location": "成都", "image_list": "", "tag_list": "桌布,餐桌改造,家居改造,奶油风", "last_modify_ts": 1743321700000, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/note_tc_004", "source_keyword": "防水桌布", "xsec_token": "token004"}
{"note_id": "note_tc_005", "type": "normal", "title": "踩坑预警⚠️这种桌布千万别买", "desc": "分享我买桌布踩过的坑。第一种棉麻桌布容易皱不好打理。第二种劣质PVC桌布有异味，质量差。第三种尺寸不对退货麻烦。建议大家买之前一定量好尺寸，选正规品牌。防水桌布选厚一点的PVC材质最靠谱。这次买的这款还不错，便宜好用不翻车。", "video_url": "", "time": 1743235200, "last_update_time": 0, "user_id": "u005", "nickname": "避坑达人E", "avatar": "https://example.com/avatar5.jpg", "liked_count": "2156", "collected_count": "987", "comment_count": "234", "share_count": "128", "ip_location": "杭州", "image_list": "https://example.com/img7.jpg,https://example.com/img8.jpg", "tag_list": "桌布,避坑,家居好物", "last_modify_ts": 1743235300000, "note_url": "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/note_tc_005", "source_keyword": "桌布", "xsec_token": "token005"}
